"فَمَا", "لَهُۥ", "مِن", "قُوَّةٖ", "وَلَا", "نَاصِرٖ"], "warsh": ["فَمَا", "لَهُۥ", "مِن", "قُوَّةٖ", "وَلَا", "نَاصِرٖۖ"], "abuamr": ["فَمَا", "لَهُۥ", "مِن", "قُوَّةٖ", "وَلَا", "نَاصِرٖ"], "reading": [], "ortho": [5], "abuamr_only": [], "en": "Then will he have no might nor any helper", "wbw": [["Then not", "famā"], ["(is) for him", "lahu"], ["any", "min"], ["power", "quwwatin"], ["and not", "walā"], ["any helper", "nāṣirin"]]}, {"hafs_aya": 11, "warsh_aya": 11, "abuamr_aya": 11, "hafs": ["وَٱلسَّمَآءِ", "ذَاتِ", "ٱلرَّجۡعِ"], "warsh": ["وَالسَّمَآءِ", "ذَاتِ", "اِ۬لرَّجْعِ"], "abuamr": ["وَاَلسَّمَآءِ", "ذَاتِ", "اِ۬لرَّجۡعِ"], "reading": [], "ortho": [0, 2], "abuamr_only": [], "en": "By the heaven which giveth the returning rain", "wbw": [["By the sky", "wal-samāi"], ["which", "dhāti"], ["returns", "l-rajʿi"]]}, {"hafs_aya": 12, "warsh_aya": 12, "abuamr_aya": 12, "hafs": ["وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ", "ذَاتِ", "ٱلصَّدۡعِ"], "warsh": ["وَالَارْضِ", "ذَاتِ", "اِ۬لصَّدْعِ"], "abuamr": ["وَاَلۡأَرۡضِ", "ذَاتِ", "اِ۬لصَّدۡعِ"], "reading": [], "ortho": [0, 2], "abuamr_only": [], "en": "And the earth which splitteth (with the growth of trees and plants)", "wbw": [["And the earth", "wal-arḍi"], ["which", "dhāti"], ["cracks open", "l-ṣadʿi"]]}, {"hafs_aya": 13, "warsh_aya": 13, "abuamr_aya": 13, "hafs": ["إِنَّهُۥ", "لَقَوۡلٞ", "فَصۡلٞ"], "warsh": ["إِنَّهُۥ", "لَقَوْلٞ", "فَصْلٞ"], "abuamr": ["إِنَّهُۥ", "لَقَوۡلٞ", "فَصۡلٞ"], "reading": [], "ortho": [1, 2], "abuamr_only": [], "en": "Lo! this (Qur'an) is a conclusive word", "wbw": [["Indeed, it", "innahu"], ["(is) surely a Word", "laqawlun"], ["decisive", "faṣlun"]]}, {"hafs_aya": 14, "warsh_aya": 14, "abuamr_aya": 14, "hafs": ["وَمَا", "هُوَ", "بِٱلۡهَزۡلِ"], "warsh": ["وَمَا", "هُوَ", "بِالْهَزْلِۖ"], "abuamr": ["وَمَا", "هُوَ", "بِالۡهَزۡلِ"], "reading": [], "ortho": [2], "abuamr_only": [], "en": "It is no pleasantry", "wbw": [["And not", "wamā"], ["it", "huwa"], ["(is) for amusement", "bil-hazli"]]}, {"hafs_aya": 15, "warsh_a